      "content": "i dont even know why i'm typing this. i just feel so incredibly empty. after the lab results came back today... i think it's finally over. all the years, the missed sleep, the debt... it was all for nothing. i don't even recognize the person i see in the mirror anymore. i'm just so tired of fighting a losing battle. i just want the noise to stop.",
